# CHALLENGE REPRODUCTION: Billion Laughs / XML Entity Expansion (XXE) Simulation
# Validates the XML parser's resilience against malicious XML payloads designed
# to exhaust memory via nested entity expansion.
# EXPECTED BEHAVIOR:
# - The parser MUST NOT crash or consume unbounded memory.
# - It should abort the parse and tag the event with an error or `_xmlparsefailure`.
filter {
  xml {
    source => "malicious_xml_payload"
    target => "parsed_xml"
    force_array => false
  }
}
